data.description: Welcome to the much desirable Oakland Trails neighborhood. This beautiful home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 and a half baths with an open floor plan perfect for entertaining. The property sits on a premium lot, overlooking the green area that can be enjoyed from the covered front porch. As you enter the home, you will be greeted with an inviting cozy living space that includes a "Chef's Dream" kitchen with a large Island, double ovens, and solid surface counter tops.  The  versatile upstairs loft offers many possibilities to entertain friends, have extra space for a home office or enjoying hobbies. All this plus direct access to the West Orange Bike Trail that leads to Downtown Winter Garden and Clermont! And don't forget about all the great community amenities like a pool, dog park and playground nearby! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home your own. Schedule a showing today and see all that Oakland Trails has to offer!
